Huge aim map by Spank.
3 things:
1).The stairs out of t spawn are un even and diffuclut to walk up.
This was made on purpose to prevent cts from easily entering t-spawn. Its hard to explain.

2). Why so much fog?
Being an out door map and huge for that matter fog was added to prevent players from shooting other player cross map.

3). Ive spotted other things that need fixing.
